long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tellq is lean & powerful in-house call center solution for small & medium enterprises. It gives companies a set of tools to handle all of the calling operations like professional call center. With Tellq companies can create entire in-house call center using web-browser: configure the best call distribution strategy to fit business needs, make & receive calls, manage & monitor workflow and easily integrate Tellq with Helpdesk or CRM you already use. 

Tellq helps companies to perfectly handle growing incoming calls, never miss a single call, make sure all calls are followed-up and maximum productivity of customer support is guaranteed. 

Tellq is created to challange old and complex call center tools by giving call operations the whole new user-friendly shape. Forget hardware, technical complexity and upfront investments. 

Learn more on our website: https://tellq.io
